# Go Conventions

## Tooling
- Format: `make fmt` (gofumpt + goimports, see Makefile:36)
- Lint: `make lint` (golangci-lint, config: .golangci.yml:1)
- Audit: `make audit` (tidy, fmt, vet, lint, test)

## Code Quality
- Always check errors (errcheck enabled: .golangci.yml:6)
- Max cyclomatic complexity: 15 (.golangci.yml:25)
- Use gofumpt (stricter than gofmt)
- Run goimports to manage imports

